              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Ba-133,Na-22,Cs-137,Y-88,Co-60 standard sources",
                "were used do define characteristic of spectrometer,",
                "which was fitted by second-degree polynomial:",
                " Egamma=a+b*X+c*X**2, where c=-(5.9+-1.6)*10**-6 .",
                " 511.0keV annihilation gamma-lines ( present in the",
                " spectrum) and 646.8keV background gamma-line( from",
                " neutron inelastic scattering in iron) were used as",
                " standard lines."
              ]
            }
          ],
